div.div: Kusanagi Kei, a high-school student living with his aunt and uncle, has an encounter with a female alien. This alien is revealed to be a new teacher at his school. Later, he is forced to marry this alien to preserve her secrets. From there, various romantically-inclined problems crop up repeatedly. (Source: Anime News Network)
A Strike Witches spin-off, featuring the 502nd Joint Fighter Wing, the Brave Witches.
